OL,3,CMichelin star chef Marcus Wareing
OL,4,Creceives MBE
OL,6,FWareing, 55, who is originally from,
OL,7,FSouthport, began his culinary career
OL,8,Faged 18, when he moved to London to
OL,9,Fwork at The Savoy.
OL,11,FThe Michelin-starred chef went on to
OL,12,Festablish several restaurants in
OL,13,FLondon, including Marcus at The
OL,14,FBerkeley in Knightsbridge, which
OL,15,Fclosed in 2023.
OL,17,FIn 2006, Wareing served a custard tart
OL,18,Fto the late Queen Elizabeth II at a
OL,19,Flunch held to celebrate her 80th
OL,20,Fbirthday.
